&lt;li&gt;选择驱动&amp;quot;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.nvidia.cn/Download/index.aspx?lang=cn&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
